802
01:00:33,320 --> 01:00:34,719
Yes.

803
01:00:34,760 --> 01:00:36,671
<i>I can't bear feeling helpless.</i>

804
01:00:37,440 --> 01:00:39,715
<i>I always think
there's something I can do.</i>

805
01:00:42,840 --> 01:00:46,037
<i>But sometimes, of course...
there's nothing.</i>

806
01:01:05,880 --> 01:01:07,791
Champagne, madam?

807
