the Luftwaffe will bomb London.

815
01:01:49,480 --> 01:01:51,357
<i>My dear, my intelligence tells me that.</i>

816
01:01:51,400 --> 01:01:54,233
<i>Then it will be dangerous
for people to congregate, won't it?</i>

817
01:01:54,280 --> 01:01:56,794
<i>Oh, Tommy! Don't be silly!</i>

818
01:01:57,640 --> 01:01:59,073
