929
01:14:51,160 --> 01:14:54,835
Mrs Henderson,
one night my bicycle went off the road

930
01:14:54,920 --> 01:14:57,832
and the next thing I knew,
I was an illusion.

931
01:14:57,880 --> 01:15:00,269
<i>Because that's all we are up there.</i>

932
01:15:00,320 --> 01:15:03,471
<i>But the odd thing is I'm still in
that river, and I want to be rescued.</i>

933
01:15:03,560 --> 01:15:07,439
<i>But not by some drum roll
or applause or a soldier's fantasy.</i>

934
01:15:08,200 --> 01:15:10,156
